EPratik%20Dawda%2C%20who%20has%20been%20with%20Rescript%20for%20over%203.5%20years%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20lead%20all%20our%20digital%20marketing%20efforts%2C%20including%20paid%20ads%2C%20content%2C%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20WhatsApp%20communications%2C%20and%20performance%20strategy.%20I%20also%20support%20B2B%20lead%20generation%20and%20collaborate%20closely%20with%20our%20web%2C%20product%2C%20and%20design%20teams%20to%20grow%20our%20online%20presence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Rescript%2C%20we%20are%20hands-on%2C%20intentional%2C%20and%20honest.%20We%20do%20not%20chase%20trends%2C%20instead%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20building%20trust%20around%20a%20genuinely%20better%20product.%20We%20aim%20to%20make%20people%20think%20differently%20about%20paper%20and%20to%20be%20memorable%20without%20being%20loud.%20Value-led%20storytelling%2C%20loyalty%2C%20and%20consistent%20engagement%20are%20central%20to%20everything%20we%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20me%2C%20the%20brand%20felt%20like%20love%20at%20first%20sight.%20It%20is%20hard%20not%20to%20believe%20in%20a%20product%20that%20just%20makes%20sense%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20world%20that%20needs%20better%20alternatives.%20Seeing%20people%20make%20the%20switch%20and%20knowing%20we%20are%20driving%20that%20momentum%20is%20what%20makes%20this%20journey%20so%20rewarding%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20social%20media%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20zero%20to%20crores%20without%20cutting%20a%20tree%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202024-25%20financial%20year%2C%20Rescript%20recorded%20Rs%205%20crore%20in%20revenue%2C%20up%20from%20Rs%203.3%20crore%20the%20previous%20year%20and%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20the%20year%20before%20that.%20They%20completed%201%2C500%20B2B%20invoices%20and%20more%20than%2010%2C000%20D2C%20orders%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20pricing%20remains%20similar%20to%20conventional%20stationery%2C%20the%20copier%20paper%20sells%20at%20Rs%20359%20%E2%80%93%20Rs%20400%2C%20notebooks%20range%20between%20Rs%2050%20and%20Rs%2085%2C%20pens%20and%20pencils%20are%20around%20Rs%20100%2C%20and%20journals%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%20499.%20For%20corporate%20gifting%2C%20customised%20bulk%20orders%20begin%20at%20500%20notebooks%20or%201%2C000%20journals%2C%20while%20smaller%20bulk%20orders%20without%20customisation%20do%20not%20have%20a%20minimum%20order%20quantity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Rescript%E2%80%99s%20standout%20offerings%20is%20its%20custom%20environmental%20impact%20report.%20After%20a%20full%20financial%20year%20of%20using%20their%20products%2C%20clients%20receive%20a%20detailed%20summary%20showing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F255790%2Fslug-ladakh-save-crores-village-dah-hanu-valley-apricots-trees-yellow-tail-moth-pest-tsering-stobdan-pest-eradication-organic-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enumber%20of%20trees%20saved%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20water%20conserved%2C%20and%20carbon%20emissions%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20one%20thing%20to%20say%20a%20product%20is%20sustainable.%20It%20is%20another%20way%20to%20show%20clients%20the%20actual%20numbers%2C%E2%80%9D%20say%20the%20co-founders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescript%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20still%20unfolding.%20But%20every%20page%20turned%20and%20every%20sheet%20printed%20is%20a%20small%20yet%20moving%20act%20of%20environmental%20responsibility.%20In%20a%20time%20when%20we%20are%20figuring%20out%20ways%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341870%2Fhygenco-first-green-hydrogen-plant-in-india-maharashtra-amit-bansal-solar-wind-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecombat%20climate%20challenges%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Naren%20and%20Ashutosh%20believe%20meaningful%20change%20can%20begin%20with%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20the%20paper%20on%20yo